===============================================================================
CouchrestModel initializer and configuration files :

  config/initializers/couchdb.rb
  config/couchdb.yml

Here you can configuration your database connection in a Rails-like way:

  development:
    protocol: 'https'
    host: sample.cloudant.com
    port: 443
    prefix: project
    suffix: test
    username: test
    password: user

Note that the name of the database is either just the prefix and suffix combined or the prefix plus any text you specifify using use_database method in your models with the suffix on the end.

===============================================================================
